<h3 id="orgddba317">Useful keys</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgddba317">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><code>C-c c m</code> - for menu</li>
<li><code>C-c c z</code> - claude-code-toggle-read-only-mode (C-c c z) - Toggle between read-only mode and normal mode in Claude buffer (useful for selecting and copying text)</li>
</ul>
</div>
